Trade_Invitation, Dear *WHO*,<p>\r\n\r\nAs an existing trader of *FESTIVAL*, you are being given an advance opportunity to book a pitch for *PLANYEAR* before we open trade applications publicly.  <p>\r\n\r\nThe dates of next year's festival are *DATES*.<p>\r\n\r\nThe location you are being offered is *LOCATION* at a price of *PRICE*.<p>\r\n\r\nIf you wish to accept the offer of a pitch at the quoted price, go to your personal *LINK* and click the purple <b>Accept</b> button near the bottom of the page.<p>\r\n\r\nYou will be asked to pay your deposit and details of how to pay will appear on screen and in your confirmation email.<p>\r\n\r\nOnce your deposit payment has been received, we will issue an invoice confirming that your pitch is secure pending your balancing payment.<p>\r\n\r\nLater we will issue a reminder that your balancing payment of &pound;*BALANCE* is due. Once your payment has arrived, we will issue an invoice confirming that your pitch is fully secure.<P>\r\n\r\nIf you wish to decline this offer, please click on your personal link and click 'decline'. <p>\r\n\r\nIf you are no longer trading, or no longer wish to be notified about trade stands at the festival click *REMOVE*.<p>\r\n\r\nPlease use this personal *LINK* to directly upload a photo of your stand/products and to write about what you sell.<p>\r\n\r\nYou can also use this link to add/correct details about your business, contact information, or change your pitch(es), update your insurance and risk assessment etc.<p>\r\n\r\nPhotos and descriptions of your goods may be visible to the public. Personal information can only be seen by the festival committee.<p> \r\n\r\nDetails of your pitch number, general trader information and particulars of setup and clear down information will appear later and be visible through the link.<p>\r\n\r\nSave the link for future use.  If you lose or forget it you will be able to request a new personal link from the website (as soon as trade applications go public).<p>\r\n\r\nIf you have any queries that are not answered by the *WEB:int/TradeFAQ.php:Trade_FAQ*, please contact *MAILTO_trade*.<p>\r\n\r\nVery much looking forward to seeing you again.<p>  \r\n\r\nWith best wishes from the *FESTIVAL* Team.
