Dance_Remind, *WHO*,\r\n\r\nWe had some issues with emails getting lost in spam filters, and we know that this year at least one email has already ended up in a spam filter. Hence, we're doing an extra check to make sure that all our invitations have arrived (obviously we don't expect you to know if you can come yet).\r\n\r\nIf you've already received an invitation from us for *FESTIVAL* *PLANYEAR*, please click <span style='background:yellow'>please could you *TICKBOX:Rec:click_this*  Invitation Seen</span>. This will automatically tick the 'invitation received' box on your web record, and take you there in case you want to edit anything else.\r\nYour web record is *LINK*.\r\n\r\nIf you haven't received an invitation, it would be much appreciated if you could check your spam folder and add 'dance@wimbornefolk.co.uk' to your address book so we can avoid emails getting lost in future. \r\n\r\nIf your invitation has completely vanished and isn't in the spam filter, let me know and I will resend it.\r\n\r\nMany thanks,\r\n\r\nDance Organisers
